Luck has ran out on a man after he tied his wife and son to use them for money ritual after planning with his friends. A video of the tragic incident has surfaced online showing the moment the suspects were caught. Luck ran out for the culprits when the woman screamed for help. Her cry attracted passerbys who approached the vehicle and rescued the woman. The incident took place in Surulere Lagos. The video also shows two men suspected to be the husband and his friend getting rough-handled by a mob. Watch video below: Source